      prosecutionSpeech: { fr: "Le 15 existait. SOS Médecins existait. Forcer une vitrine est un délit, peu importe la cause. Si on accepte ça, chaque urgence familiale devient un permis de voler.", en: "Emergency lines existed. House calls existed. Forcing a window is a crime, regardless of cause. Accepting this turns every family emergency into a license to steal." },
